d
d=\sqrt{(x_2-x_1)^2 + (y_2-y_1)^2} = (\sqrt{1023^2+767^2})p
d = 100 { \sqrt{1023^2+767^2} \over \sqrt{1024^2+768^2} }  \approx 99.81
